# Release / toolchain artifacts
cyrius-*.tar.gz
*.tar.gz
SHA256SUMS

# Resolved stdlib (patra model): the whole dir is generated — `cyrius deps`
# materializes the deps closure from the pinned toolchain on a clean checkout
# (CI does exactly this); `cyrius lib sync` refreshes a local copy to the pin.
# Never commit lib/ — a tracked-but-incomplete lib shadows the pinned snapshot
# and breaks `cyrius deps` (the 0.6.0 ganita.cyr CI failure).
/lib/

